{{template "base" .}}

{{define "content"}}
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Transylvanian Retreat</h1>
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="text-justify mt-3" style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;">
                            Welcome to <strong>Transylvanian Retreat</strong>, your home away from home nestled in the heart of the Carpathian Mountains in Brașov, Romania. Our boutique hotel is designed to provide you with a unique blend of rustic charm and modern comfort, making it the perfect getaway for anyone seeking tranquility and adventure.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-justify mt-3" style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;">
                            Our location offers breathtaking views of the surrounding mountains and easy access to the historic sites of Brașov, including the famous Black Church and the charming old town. Whether you're here for a romantic weekend, a family vacation, or a solo retreat, Transylvanian Retreat promises an unforgettable experience.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-justify mt-3" style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;">
                            Each room at our retreat is thoughtfully designed with your comfort in mind, featuring cozy furnishings, comfortable linens, and all the amenities you need to feel at home. Enjoy a relaxing morning with breakfast in bed, take a stroll through our beautiful garden, or simply unwind by the fireplace in our lounge.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-justify mt-3 mb-4" style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;">
                            At Transylvanian Retreat, we pride ourselves on offering personalized service to ensure your stay is as enjoyable as possible. Our friendly staff is always on hand to assist with any needs or recommendations you may have. Discover the beauty and charm of Brașov and create lasting memories with us.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{{end}}
